summary: Custom model of Witcher\'s Silver sword
descriptionHtml: Custom model of the Witcher\'s Silver sword from the Witcher RPG games. Made by myself for a competiton at another site :) It currently replaces the default silver sword in the game, although the nif\'s and dds files can be found inside the archive for anyone that wants to make unique objects etc :) Or just take the art and use it for something else.
author: Kimono
